{"tid":1445591,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間野我dllm 一路食一路講班示威者拉喇拉喇 拉哂佢啦","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T19:21:36.000Z","uid":167024,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db6563e4c0de322a5789c67d8b8c6c1933da6513","tid":1445591,"uid":167024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:22:38.000Z","msg":"間唔時都會去食 韓國人老細<br />\n今晚落左去食 你老味 一路大聲講班示威者搞亂 快啲拉哂班人 一路嘻哈大聲笑 韓國人老細都見到我黑面叫佢地細聲啲 但都繼續 即刻食唔落埋單走 以後唔會再食！好L嬲 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8V55d8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8V55d8v.png&h=ebaef675&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENvXPG2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENvXPG2.png&h=67571cb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7016c45bee3abee96b4d69d6feb382e3d4133849","tid":1445591,"uid":126046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:39:21.000Z","msg":"詳細啲<br />\n<br />\n咩名<br />\n位置<br />\nOpen rice link"},{"pid":"98fb3ece94dda30841aba18d76f6d3eadbfe229b","tid":1445591,"uid":8435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-韓國料理-荃灣-韓國菜-沙律-r511553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%96%99%E7%90%86-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%9C-%E6%B2%99%E5%BE%8B-r511553&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16Rc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=83f0991b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-韓國料理-荃灣-韓國菜-沙律-r511553</a>"},{"pid":"427a87d79e753ad1d2dfdd8710e4fb624e0750a7","tid":1445591,"uid":60164,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:18.000Z","msg":"韓仔野做開咩客咪咩老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大撚把港豬迷泡過日晨<br />\n咩身邊野都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b639bff07249277d23efd223e4f81c3fc00ead83",